name: Unnamed Sock Game
description:
I don't support sexism, racism, homophobia and other stuff that shouldn't be supported.

In this game, you are sock. In hell. Your only task is to proceed no matter what.  And you probably won't even make it to the second level on your first attempt because hell wants you to suffer. And it will make you suffer.

Unless you're very skilled, i guess

Also music slaps imo
